          <h1>Refund Policy</h1>
          
          <p>At lnksbot, we strive to provide a high-quality service that meets your needs. This Refund Policy outlines the conditions under which we issue refunds for our subscription services.</p>
          
          <h2>1. Subscription Refunds</h2>
          <p>We offer the following refund options for our subscription plans:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>14-Day Money-Back Guarantee:</strong> If you are not satisfied with our service, you may request a full refund within 14 days of your initial subscription purchase. This applies only to first-time subscribers.</li>
            <li><strong>Pro-rated Refunds:</strong> If you cancel your subscription after the 14-day period but before the end of your billing cycle, we may issue a pro-rated refund for the unused portion of your subscription at our discretion.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>2. Eligibility for Refunds</h2>
          <p>To be eligible for a refund, you must meet the following criteria:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your account must be in good standing.</li>
            <li>You must submit your refund request within the applicable refund period.</li>
            <li>For the 14-day money-back guarantee, you must be a first-time subscriber to the plan for which you are requesting a refund.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>3. Non-Refundable Items</h2>
          <p>The following are not eligible for refunds:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Subscription renewals after the initial 14-day period (except for pro-rated refunds as described above).</li>
            <li>Any add-on services or features purchased separately from the main subscription.</li>
            <li>Accounts that have violated our Terms of Service.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2>4. How to Request a Refund</h2>
          <p>To request a refund, please contact our support team at support@lnksbot.com with the following information:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your account email address</li>
            <li>Date of purchase</li>
            <li>Reason for requesting a refund</li>
            <li>Any relevant order or transaction information</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We will process your refund request within 5 business days and notify you of the outcome.</p>
          
          <h2>5. Refund Processing</h2>
          <p>Approved refunds will be processed using the same payment method used for the original purchase. Depending on your payment provider, it may take 5-10 business days for the refund to appear in your account.</p>
          
          <h2>6. Plan Downgrades</h2>
          <p>If you downgrade your subscription plan, the change will take effect at the end of your current billing cycle. We do not issue refunds for the remaining time on your current plan when you downgrade.</p>
          
          <h2>7. Free Trial Conversions</h2>
          <p>If you convert from a free trial to a paid subscription, the 14-day money-back guarantee period begins on the date of conversion to the paid plan, not the start date of your free trial.</p>
          
          <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Refund Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date. You are advised to review this policy periodically for any changes.</p>
          
          <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about this Refund Policy, please contact us at support@lnksbot.com.</p>
          
